summary: The save of Imperial race hero in the very beginning of the game
descriptionHtml:
Valeria  The Imperial War Girl Savegame

Another savegame  now she is an Imperial

You will need these modifications for proper appearance
Beautiful Girl http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=475
No Dirty Bodies http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=18
Thanks to srimk and viperslayer for mods!


Just put the file into your Saves folder
You can easily change the character using showracemenu console command


Please tell me how it works in your game because I have the Russian version of Skyrim
Enjoy!
